\par After Black played at 1, if White answers at A then Black \cf1\b gains\cf0\b0  \cf1\b sente\cf0\b0 .
\par In a situation like this, normally White plays elsewhere and Black gets the right to play the next sente moves. Therefore it is possible to count the value of A (on the main diagram) as \cf2\b gote X points\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par
\par }
